<resolution-body style="traditional" id="H360261C2CCA84E47A68089A6DA858E4F"> 
<section display-inline="yes-display-inline" section-type="undesignated-section" id="HBAB95AA10AF1429BAF5F18F48DC4D713"><text>That the following members are, and are hereby, elected to the following standing committees:</text> 

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HAG00"> Committee on Agriculture</committee-name>—</header><text>Mr. Cassidy.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HBU00"> Committee on the Budget</committee-name>—</header><text>Mr. Aderholt of Alabama, to rank after Mr. Nunes of California, and Mr. Harper.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HIF00"> Committee on Energy and Commerce</committee-name>—</header><text>Mr. Scalise.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HGO00"> Committee on Oversight and Government Reform</committee-name>—</header><text>Mr. Schock.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HSY00"> Committee on Science and Technology</committee-name>—</header><text>Mr. Smith of Nebraska, to rank after Mr. Bilbray.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HPW00"> Committee on Transportation and Infrastructure</committee-name>— </header><text>Mr. Guthrie, Mr. Cao, Mr. Schock, and Mr. Olson, all to rank after Mr. Latta.</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

<committee-appointment-paragraph><header><committee-name committee-id="HVR00"> Committee on Veterans' Affairs</committee-name>— </header><text>Mr. Lamborn, to rank after Mr. Bilbray, and Mr. Roe of Tennessee .</text></committee-appointment-paragraph>

</section> 
</resolution-body> 
<attestation><attestation-group><attestor display="no">Lorraine C. Miller,</attestor><role>Clerk.</role></attestation-group></attestation>
</resolution> 
